{"tid":2155714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港康碼急需正名「送中碼」","createTime":"2020-08-14T03:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T05:46:20.000Z","uid":154702,"like":200,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c68763aa653126d531ea9ee741b84aba1776f8","tid":2155714,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:31:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">正名非常重要</span></span></strong><br />\n國安惡法既發展底下<br />\n香港人以港康碼送中既日子不遠矣<br />\n<br />\n送中碼明顯只為未來監控鋪路<br />\n防疫效果成疑<br />\n點解喺你幫襯嗰刻收銀呀姐量你體溫<br />\n會比你唔知幾多日之前了喉嚨<br />\n等化驗而得出既結果新鮮有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3448a1cb08cf20c4f32f19ef9efafab8a5acc76a","tid":2155714,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f949fe0023ae7c25fcc1c5eeffd316654ad092","tid":2155714,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2ad01e44fb716860bea3a958c432f5b4bcfc15a0","tid":2155714,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"民主派總唔總辭已經唔再重要，健康碼（社會信用評級）殺到埋身<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2155670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2155670</a>"},{"pid":"e8cf3e8a474907f69eb4a34fc0bb98f9533c6bc2","tid":2155714,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"（千祈咪做檢測）一人留DNA，全家十八代奶野。廢老做檢測，後生比人拉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l